{"tid":393983,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩帥評車路士：只懂得玩防反","createTime":"2017-09-09T14:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T15:03:06.000Z","uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9108358d725696498c9630f3c550143a9998dc6d","tid":393983,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"日前，在曼聯對陣史篤城的新聞記者會上，曼聯教練摩連奴表示，干地取得聯賽冠軍是因為打「防守足球」，並稱自己不會為了奪冠而效仿干地的做法。<br />\n<br />\n　　摩連奴在記者會上這樣說道：「我們知道如果你從一個&lsquo;好事者&rsquo;的角度去看待上個賽季的聯賽冠軍，你會發現他們並沒有打出攻勢足球。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「他們踢得是防守足球，是角球進攻。所以根據以上結果，這才是英超冠軍的方法。」<br />\n<br />\n　　但是摩帥似乎對於干地的打法並不十分讚同，他認為干地所施行的3-4-3陣型，幾乎是就是7個人在後場進行防守。<br />\n<br />\n　　「<span style=\"color: red;\">但要是你問我我們是否會安排7個人在後場，像某些球隊做的那樣5個人再加上2個防守中場？不會的。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n　　摩連奴補充道：「我們要試著去踢得漂亮並且獲得入球。但是如果我們的對手強於我們且勢不可擋，那我們可能會為了比賽結果而改變我們的踢球方式。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「要是有一天為了贏波我們必須要踢防守足球，那麼我會的。」"},{"pid":"777e527fa8b59aa2a64252a5bf915be296d32a86","tid":393983,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec8282d34a417cdbcfd676f58320b200f551897","tid":393983,"uid":17832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T14:54:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2e7b7563569cefd3f6a96cb35fa5a4e148654a4","tid":393983,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T14:56:43.000Z","msg":"最後個句冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49e787d2b2e2c020f28410e3ae0273233e3a07f","tid":393983,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T14:58:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d12423e61f523f4184e372f9c4f5ab683df650bb","tid":393983,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>丫你條友今季入多兩粒就咁多嗲</blockquote><br />\n同張一樣無恥，講到自己冇份咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8351bbc7e33d4c254d566ac597f62149f68a691c","tid":393983,"uid":9706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"2014-15<br />\n1\tChelsea (C)\tGF 73  GA 32  GD +41  PTS 87<br />\n<br />\n2016-17<br />\n1\tChelsea (C)\tGF 85  GA 33  GD +52  PTS 93<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}